Looking For Good Roblox Creators!
We are looking for Roblox creators who are good at; building, drawing/animation, or coding! We are currently working on a game and need your help!

What The Game Is About!
What the game is going to be is a Papermorph Roleplay with the animation/art style of 20s-50s Animation. It's going to be a bit cutesy with a scary undertone mixed in along with some secrets and lore!

How To Join The Team!
If this is the kind of stuff you are looking for and are wishing to try your hand at joing the team, please take our survey that is posted in the post. Can't wait to have you on our team and have a great day!
